  "prompt": "How widely accepted are credit cards at small businesses and restaurants in Malta?",
  "response": "Credit cards are generally widely accepted in Malta, especially in urban areas and tourist destinations. However, some smaller businesses and restaurants, particularly in more rural areas or traditional establishments, may prefer cash payments. Visa and Mastercard are the most commonly accepted cards, with American Express being less widely used. It's always a good idea to carry some cash as a backup, especially when visiting smaller establishments or local eateries.",
